%% MON Platform — Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated: 2026-04-20

sequenceDiagram
    participant Fan as Fan (Browser)
    participant UI as Next.js Frontend
    participant ZK as zkLogin Service
    participant Backend as Backend / Sponsor
    participant Sui as Sui Blockchain
    participant Seal as Seal Protocol
    participant Walrus as Walrus Storage
    participant Indexer as Custom Indexer
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    %% === Fan Onboarding ===
    Note over Fan, Sui: Fan Onboarding Flow

    Fan->>UI: Click "Enter Gate"
    UI->>ZK: OAuth login (Google/Apple)
    ZK-->>UI: Ephemeral keypair + ZK proof
    UI->>Backend: Request sponsored tx (join_gate)
    Backend->>Sui: Sponsored tx: mon_gate::join_gate()
    Sui-->>Sui: Mint MonPass (owned by fan)
    Sui-->>Sui: Emit MonPassMintedEvent
    Sui-->>Backend: Tx success
    Backend-->>UI: MonPass ID
    UI-->>Fan: "Welcome, 門徒!"

    %% === Quest Completion ===
    Note over Fan, DB: Quest Completion Flow

    Fan->>UI: Complete quiz / scan QR
    UI->>Backend: Submit quest answer + proof
    Backend->>Backend: Validate answer, sign proof
    Backend->>Sui: Sponsored tx: quest::complete_quest(sig)
    Sui-->>Sui: Verify sig + role
    Sui-->>Sui: add_xp() → auto rank check
    Sui-->>Sui: mint_badge() if applicable
    Sui-->>Sui: Emit QuestCompletedEvent, RankUpEvent
    Sui-->>Backend: Tx success
    Backend-->>UI: Updated XP, rank, badge
    UI-->>Fan: "Level Up! New Badge earned!"

    %% === Content Unlock ===
    Note over Fan, Walrus: Content Gating Flow

    Fan->>UI: Request gated video
    UI->>Seal: Request decryption (MonPass ref)
    Seal->>Sui: check_access(policy, gate, pass, tier)
    Sui-->>Seal: Access approved (rank meets tier)
    Seal-->>UI: Decryption key
    UI->>Walrus: Fetch encrypted blob
    Walrus-->>UI: Ciphertext
    UI->>UI: Decrypt locally
    UI-->>Fan: Play video

    %% === Monban AI Interaction ===
    Note over Fan, Sui: Monban AI Flow

    Fan->>UI: Chat with Monban
    UI->>Backend: Message to AI
    Backend->>Backend: AI generates response
    Backend->>Backend: If action triggered, sign with Monban key
    Backend->>Sui: monban::monban_complete_quest(sig)
    Sui-->>Sui: Verify Monban identity + sig
    Sui-->>Sui: Grant badge / XP
    Sui-->>Sui: Emit MonbanActionEvent
    Sui-->>Backend: Tx success
    Backend-->>UI: AI response + achievement notification
    UI-->>Fan: "門番 grants you '師父認可' badge!"

    %% === Indexer Pipeline ===
    Note over Sui, DB: Indexer Pipeline

    Sui->>Indexer: Stream checkpoints (events)
    Indexer->>DB: Process & store (passes, quests, leaderboards)
    UI->>DB: Query leaderboard / history (REST API)
    DB-->>UI: Aggregated data
